data.description: Discover the potential of this charming ranch-style home nestled in the vibrant and up-and-coming community of Mableton, GA. Located in a prime area with easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment, this property offers the perfect blend of convenience and tranquility. Boasting ample space, a private lot ideal for gardening or relaxation, and a full basement for additional storage or future expansion, this home presents a unique opportunity for investors or DIY enthusiasts. While it requires some updating, the asking price reflects the needed repairs, making it an affordable option with plenty of potential. Say goodbye to monthly HOA fees and embrace the freedom to customize and enhance your property as you see fit. Don't miss out on this opportunity to transform this fixer-upper into your dream home. Contact us today to schedule a private showing and explore the possibilities that await you in the thriving community of Mableton, GA!
